From d75f63b3b36179cbba45faf802aa0bdfe5e18463 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 06:06:54 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: subscription CRUD, superadmin cross-org queries,
 employee/role crash fixes

Backend:
- Add subscription plan create/update/delete endpoints (superadmin only)
- Add SubscriptionPlanCreate and SubscriptionPlanUpdate schemas
- Expand subscription CRUD with create, update, soft_delete operations
- Roles API: allow superadmin to query roles for any org via ?organization_id=
- Users API: allow superadmin to list users for any org via ?organization_id=
- Both endpoints use _resolve_org_id() helper for JWT/query param resolution

Frontend:
- SubscriptionPlansView: complete rewrite with create/edit/delete modals
- SubscriptionPlansView: add better error handling (shows actual error messages)
- SubscriptionPlansView: superadmin sees inactive plans and management buttons
- EmployeesView: add isSuperAdminNoOrg guard (shows notice instead of crash)
- RolesView: add isSuperAdminNoOrg guard (shows notice instead of crash)
- Both views skip API calls when superadmin has no org context
